channel.title: Help with adding commands into client.java serverside
channel.description: Hiya, heres my problem. Every time I add a command, and im writing the command into client.java right, it doesnt work right... I made a command for ::admin, to tele to an admin area, I added the string of code to client.java and compiled and ran...But it doesnt work on the client. This also happens when i add other stuff into client.java..such as a custom special attack to a custom weapon....Any helpful tips appreciated :)
